in this artical we will learn how to configure our rhel 7 to ansible. there is few configuration lines which will have to do. 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
follow the following steps
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. power on your rhel 7 machine in vmware 
2. connecte internet with rhel 7
3. #cd /tmp
4. #wget https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
5. #yum install epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
6. #cd
7. #cd /etc/yum.repos.d/
8. #yum repolist
9. #yum install -y ansible
10. #yum install -y htop
